Modul de.hitec.nhplus
Package de.hitec.nhplus.model

Klasse Employee

java.lang.Object
de.hitec.nhplus.model.Person
de.hitec.nhplus.model.Employee
public class Employee extends Person
The Employee class represents an employee with a unique employee ID, role, status, and additional properties. This class extends the Person class, inheriting its properties for name and surname.

    • Employee

      public Employee(String name, String surname, String role, String lockDateInTenYears, String status, String phoneNumber)
      Constructs a new Employee with the specified details, excluding the employee ID.
      Parameter:
      name - the first name of the employee
      surname - the last name of the employee
      role - the role of the employee in the organization
      lockDateInTenYears - the lock date in ten years
      status - the current status of the employee (e.g., Active, Inactive)
      phoneNumber - the phone number of the employee

    • Employee

      name - the first name of the employee
      surname - the last name of the employee
      role - the role of the employee in the organization
